{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_64","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc \"sed -n '1,220p' ISSUE_COMMENTS.md && sed -n '1,260p' PR_COMMENTS.md\"","aggregated_output":"Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n\nSummary:\n- `GO:0046179 keto-D-gluconate biosynthetic process` has been obsoleted because the issue noted no annotations or cross-references.\n- Existing obsolete stanzas for `GO:0019584`, `GO:0046180`, and `GO:0046181` were cleaned to follow GO obsoletion metadata conventions.\n- `GO:0019584` retains `consider` references to `GO:0034194` and `GO:0034195`; the EcoCyc annotation should be moved to `GO:0034195` as requested.\n- `GO:0046181` retains `replaced_by: GO:0019524`.\n\nValidation passed with `make -C src/ontology travis_build`.\n# Summary\n\nAddressed issue #31978 by completing the requested carbohydrate process obsoletions and cleaning the affected obsolete stanzas in `src/ontology/go-edit.obo`.\n\nChanges made:\n- Obsoleted `GO:0046179 keto-D-gluconate biosynthetic process` with the issue tracker link and an obsoletion comment noting no annotations or cross-references.\n- Removed synonyms and logical axioms from obsolete terms, following current GO obsoletion practice.\n- Removed `replaced_by: GO:0046179` from `GO:0046180`, since `GO:0046179` is now obsolete and should not be the active replacement target.\n- Kept `GO:0019584` with `consider: GO:0034194` and `consider: GO:0034195`, matching the split between D- and L-galactonate catabolic process terms.\n- Kept `GO:0046181` with `replaced_by: GO:0019524`.\n- Fixed the typo `grouing` -> `grouping` in the `GO:0019584` obsoletion comment.\n\n# Rationale\n\n`GO:0019584`, `GO:0046180`, and `GO:0046181` were already obsolete in the local ontology, but retained synonyms that obsolete terms should not keep. `GO:0046179` was still active and had a biosynthetic-process logical definition; the issue comment explicitly noted that this term has no annotations and no cross-references, so it was obsoleted with no replacement.\n\nBecause `GO:0046179` is now obsolete, `GO:0046180` cannot safely retain it as a `replaced_by` target. `GO:0046181` retains the requested active replacement `GO:0019524`.\n\n# Validation\n\n- Pre-change validation: `make -C src/ontology travis_build` passed.\n- Post-change validation: `make -C src/ontology travis_build` passed.\n- `git diff --check -- src/ontology/go-edit.obo` passed.\n\nAnnotation impact note: I attempted the required OAK/AmiGO direct annotation check with `runoak -i amigo: associations`, but the local `runoak` installation failed before executing the query due to a Python dependency mismatch: `AttributeError: type object 'Format' has no attribute 'JSON'`. The issue itself states the known annotation impact: one EcoCyc annotation to `GO:0019584` should be moved to `GO:0034195`; `GO:0046180` and `GO:0046179` have no annotations, and `GO:0046181` should be replaced by `GO:0019524`.\n\n# Checklist\n\n- [x] PLAN: Issue title, body, and comment reviewed; requested obsoletions and replacements identified.\n- [x] PRE-VALIDATION: Current ontology validated before edits.\n- [x] RESEARCH: N/A; no new biological references or PMIDs were introduced.\n- [x] TERM-SEARCH: Existing GO terms and references checked with `obo-grep.pl`.\n- [x] DESIGN-PATTERNS: Relevant catabolic and biosynthetic process patterns checked; obsolete terms retain no logical definitions.\n- [x] EDITS: Terms were edited through `obo-checkout.pl` / `obo-checkin.pl`.\n- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: Obsolete terms have no `is_a`, `relationship`, or `intersection_of` axioms; `GO:0046180` no longer points to an obsolete replacement.\n- [x] SPECIALIZED-EDITS: Term obsoletion workflow applied. Chemical-entity concerns were considered; no CHEBI IDs or chemical definitions were changed.\n- [x] METADATA: Obsolete terms include namespace, obsolete definition text, obsoletion comment, `is_obsolete: true`, and issue tracker link where applicable.\n- [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: `make -C src/ontology travis_build` passed after edits.\n- [x] REFERENCE-VALIDATION: N/A; no new references were added.\n- [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: Local commit `be66096` contains only `src/ontology/go-edit.obo`.\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
